Package org.primaresearch.web.gwt.client.ui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DocumentImageListener
    Listener for document image events.
    DocumentImageSource
    Interface for classes that provide access to document images.
    MouseScrollPanel.MouseHandlerExtension
    Mouse handling extension for MouseScrollPanel
    MouseScrollPanel.ScrollListener  
    RenderStyles
    Interface for rendering style factories.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DocumentImageLoader
    Helper class to load document images from the server.
    MouseScrollPanel
    Scroll panel handling mouse events to enable panning by dragging the mouse.

    The first widget that is added to the panel is used for the scrolling.
    RenderStyles.RenderStyle
    Rendering style (including line colour, fill colour and line width).
